Name: Blockicker
About the game: Blockicker is a game where a young boy falls into a cave containing many block puzzles, and need to solve them to get out of it! The difference of Blockicker to many other games is that our hero needs to kick blocks of several shapes, and the difficulty of the game increases in each level!
